<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
<head>
 <title>Givelist</title>
 <meta charSet="utf-8"/>
 <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
 <meta name="description" content="Here is a description of what Givelist is all about."/>
 <link href="<%= url('styles/normalize.scss') %>" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
 <link href="<%= url('styles/main.scss') %>" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>

<body class="no-scroll">
 <div id="content">
  <header>
   <a href="/"><span class="logo"></span></a>
   <nav>
    <a class="button primary" href="#">Sign Up</a>
    <a class="button" href="#">Log In</a>
   </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
   <section id="dashboard">
    <div class="row profile">
     <img src="<%= url('/images/photos/portrait.jpg') %>">
     <div class="profile-details">
      <h3>Aubri French</h3>
      <a href="mailto:aubrifrench@gmail.com">aubrifrench@gmail.com</a>
      <p>987 Main St.</p>
      <p>San Diego, CA 92110</p>
      <p>(858) 431-9559</p>
     </div>
     <div class="bio">
       <p>Hey there! I'm Aubri, and this is the bio on my Givelist profile. I enjoy giving gifts to people and promoting non-profit organizations, which help make the world a better place. Also included in my interests are pizza, puppies, and pool parties! The three P's! Ha!</p>
     </div>
    </div>



    <div class="row dashboard-controls">
     <ul>
      <li class="active">
       <button>Wishlists</button>
      </li>

      <li>
       <button>Orders</button>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>



    <div class="row list-of-wishlists-and-orders">
     <ul>
       <li class="add-item">
        <div class="tile folded-corner">
         <div class="container">
          <span class="wishlist-icon"></span>
          <h5>Add Wishlist</h5>
         </div>
        </div>
       </li>

      <li>
       <div class="tile folded-corner">
        <img src="<%= url('/images/textures/wishlist.jpg') %>">
       </div>
       <h5>Jacob's Birthday List 2018</h5>
      </li>

      <li class="active">
       <div class="tile">
        <img src="<%= url('/images/textures/wishlist.jpg') %>">
       </div>
       <h5>Wedding Registry</h5>
      </li>

      <li>
       <div class="tile folded-corner">
        <img src="<%= url('/images/textures/wishlist.jpg') %>">
       </div>
       <h5>This is a really long list title just to demonstrate the automatic ellipsis line clamp.</h5>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>



    <div class="row view-wishlist">
     <div>
      <h2>Wedding Registry</h2>
      <div class="hgroup">
       <button>View as Guest</button>
       <button>Make Public</button>
       <fieldset>
        <span>Sharable Link:</span>
        <input type="text" value="http://givelist.com/list/j8HE8q9Vbj1Y">
       </fieldset>
      </div>

      <ul class="wishlist-items">
       <li class="wishlist-item add-item">
        <div class="container">
         <span class="gift-icon"></span>
         <h4>Add Item</h4>
        </div>
       </li>

       <li class="wishlist-item">
        <div class="image-container">
         <img src="<%= url('/images/photos/products/toaster.jpg') %>">
        </div>
        <div class="text-container">
         <h4>AmazonBasics KT-3680 2-Slice Toaster</h4>
         <p>$29.99</p>
         <p>This toaster would make a nice addition to our kitchen, which is why you should totally buy it! How else are we going to make hot bread, you know??"</p>
        </div>
       </li>

       <li class="wishlist-item">
        <div class="image-container">
         <img src="<%= url('/images/photos/products/hot-pot.jpg') %>">
        </div>
        <div class="text-container">
         <h4>Instant Pot LUX60V3 V3 6 Qt 6-in-1 Multi-Use Programmable Hot Pot</h4>
         <p>$79.99</p>
         <p>10 quart size.</p>
        </div>
       </li>

       <li class="wishlist-item">
        <div class="image-container">
         <img src="<%= url('/images/photos/products/toaster.jpg') %>">
        </div>
        <div class="text-container">
         <h4>AmazonBasics KT-3680 2-Slice Toaster</h4>
         <p>$29.99</p>
         <p>This toaster would make a nice addition to our kitchen, which is why you should totally buy it! How else are we going to make hot bread, you know??"</p>
        </div>
       </li>

       <li class="wishlist-item">
        <div class="hover-content">
         <span class="close-icon"></span>
         <div class="button-container">
          <button class="primary"><h4>View</h4></button>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
         <img src="<%= url('/images/photos/products/hot-pot.jpg') %>">
        </div>
        <div class="text-container">
         <h4>Instant Pot LUX60V3 V3 6 Qt 6-in-1 Multi-Use Programmable Hot Pot</h4>
         <p>$79.99</p>
         <p>10 quart size.</p>
        </div>
       </li>
      </ul>
     </div>
    </div>
   </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
   <ul>
    <li>Â© 2018 Givelist, Inc.</li>
    <li><a href="#">Legal</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
   </ul>
  </footer>

  <div class="modal-background">
   <%= yield %>
  </div>

 </div>
</body>
</html>